name: Michael Wonz
description: I am a kind, thoughtful and friendly person. I relate easily to people and enjoy spending time with my friends. In my leisure time I like walking, going to the beach, watching movies and taking photos. I have a positive outlook on life. I’ve been told I am passionate, caring, sincere, classy, deep, genuine, playful, affectionate. I’m sensual and love spending time with my woman, sharing some unforgettable moments.
